#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/networking/ssl_certificates.rst:4
msgid "SSL certificates"
msgstr "SSL证书"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/networking/ssl_certificates.rst:7
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "简介"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/networking/ssl_certificates.rst:9
msgid ""
"It is often desired to use SSL connections for communications to avoid \"man "
"in the middle\" attacks. Godot has a connection wrapper, :ref:`StreamPeerSSL "
"<class_StreamPeerSSL>`, which can take a regular connection and add security "
"around it. The :ref:`HTTPClient <class_HTTPClient>` class also supports "
"HTTPS by using this same wrapper."
msgstr ""
"通常希望使用SSL连接进行通信，以避免 ``中间人`` 攻击。Godot有一个连接包装器，"
"即 :ref:`StreamPeerSSL <class_StreamPeerSSL>`，它可以建立常规连接并在其周围增"
"加安全性。:ref:`HTTPClient <class_HTTPClient>` 类也通过使用相同的包装器来支持"
"HTTPS。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/networking/ssl_certificates.rst:16
msgid ""
"For SSL to work, certificates need to be provided. A .crt file must be "
"specified in the project settings:"
msgstr ""
"为了使SSL起作用，需要提供证书。一个 ``.crt`` 文件必须在项目设置中指定："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/networking/ssl_certificates.rst:21
msgid ""
"This file should contain any number of public certificates in `PEM format "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Privacy-enhanced_Electronic_Mail>`__."
msgstr ""
"该文件应包含 `PEM 格式 <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Privacy-"
"enhanced_Electronic_Mail>`__ 的任意数量的公共证书。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/networking/ssl_certificates.rst:24
msgid ""
"Of course, remember to add .crt as filter so the exporter recognizes this "
"when exporting your project."
msgstr "当然，请记住将 ``.crt`` 添加为过滤器，以便导出器在导出项目时识别出它。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/networking/ssl_certificates.rst:29
msgid "There are two ways to obtain certificates:"
msgstr "有两种获取证书的方法："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/networking/ssl_certificates.rst:32
msgid "Approach 1: self signed cert"
msgstr "方法1：自签名证书"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/networking/ssl_certificates.rst:34
msgid ""
"The first approach is the simplest: generate a private and public key pair "
"and add the public key (in PEM format) to the .crt file. The private key "
"should go to your server."
msgstr ""
"第一种方法是最简单的：生成一对私钥和公用密钥对，并将公钥（以 ``PEM`` 格式）放"
"入 ``.crt`` 文件中。私钥应转到您的服务器。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/networking/ssl_certificates.rst:38
msgid ""
"OpenSSL has `some documentation <https://raw.githubusercontent.com/openssl/"
"openssl/master/doc/HOWTO/keys.txt>`__ about this. This approach also **does "
"not require domain validation** nor requires you to spend a considerable "
"amount of money in purchasing certificates from a CA."
msgstr ""
"OpenSSL对此有 `一些文档 <https://raw.githubusercontent.com/openssl/openssl/"
"master/doc/HOWTO/keys.txt>`__。此方法既 **不需要域名验证**，也不需要您花费大"
"量金钱从CA购买证书。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/networking/ssl_certificates.rst:45
msgid "Approach 2: CA cert"
msgstr "方法2：CA证书"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/networking/ssl_certificates.rst:47
msgid ""
"The second approach consists of using a certificate authority (CA) such as "
"Verisign, Geotrust, etc. This is a more cumbersome process, but it's more "
"\"official\" and ensures your identity is clearly represented."
msgstr ""
"第二种方法包括使用证书颁发机构（CA），例如Verisign，Geotrust等。这是一个比较"
"繁琐的过程，但它更 ``正式``，可确保您的身份得到清晰表示。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/networking/ssl_certificates.rst:52
msgid ""
"Unless you are working with large companies or corporations, or need to "
"connect to someone else's servers (i.e., connecting to Google or some other "
"REST API provider via HTTPS), this method is not as useful."
msgstr ""
"除非您与大型公司合作，或者需要连接到其他人的服务器（例如，通过HTTPS连接到"
"Google或其他REST API提供程序），否则此方法就没有用。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/networking/ssl_certificates.rst:56
msgid ""
"Also, when using a CA issued cert, **you must enable domain validation**, to "
"ensure the domain you are connecting to is the one intended, otherwise any "
"website can issue any certificate in the same CA and it will work."
msgstr ""
"另外，使用CA颁发的证书时，**您必须启用域验证**，以确保您要连接的域名是预期使"
"用的域名，否则任何网站都可以在同一CA中颁发任何证书，并且可以正常工作。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/networking/ssl_certificates.rst:61
msgid ""
"If you are using Linux, you can use the supplied certs file, generally "
"located in:"
msgstr "如果您使用的是Linux，则可以使用提供的certs文件，该文件通常位于："

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/networking/ssl_certificates.rst:68
msgid ""
"This file allows HTTPS connections to virtually any website (i.e., Google, "
"Microsoft, etc.)."
msgstr "此文件允许HTTPS连接到几乎任何网站（即Google，Microsoft等）。"

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/tutorials/networking/ssl_certificates.rst:71
msgid ""
"Or pick any of the more specific certificates there if you are connecting to "
"a specific one."
msgstr "或者，如果要连接到特定网站，请选择任何更加具体的证书。"
